<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV21">
<l>cūṭṭunaṉ mālaikaḷ tūyaṉa vēntiviṇ ṇōrkaṇaṉṉī</l>
<l>rāṭṭiyan tūpan tarāniṟka vēyaṅkōr māyaiyiṉā</l>
<l>līṭṭiya veṇṇey toṭuvuṇṇap pōntimi lēṟṟuvaṉkūṉ</l>
<l>kōṭṭiṭai yāṭiṉai kūttaṭa lāyartaṅ kompiṉukkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>While celestials keep offering good garlands that are pure to adorn [you],</l>
<l>bathing [you] in good water, giving pretty incense, did you go there by magic,</l>
<l>to dig into [and] eat the stored butter, did you dance the dance</l>
<l>between the humped bull’s strong curved horns for the twig of the murderous cowherds?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
